data.description: Serenity and calm with this house, located in a circle with the best of both worlds with no backyard neighbors but a great community of neighbors. It’s pre-inspected, like new construction with advanced amenities and the future in mind. The solar panel system will impact your monthly utility costs and save you from those occasional power outages when your major appliances are typically down. The basement is so far along and framed out for 2 additional bedrooms plus a working ½ bathroom. Kitchen pantry is a must these days, plus a drop zone and main floor laundry. Primary bedroom with dual sinks, walk-in closet and a spacious room is all a part of any homeowner’s wants and needs. The large windows in the living room allow you to dream out into the backyard’s wooded area, lots of bird watching and an occasional golfer. It’s the perfect drive from Offutt AFB, Bellevue, or Plattsmouth. See it today to see if it’s your next move.
